        rdfs:comment        "The steps involved in proprotein convertase PCSK9-induced degradation of VLDLR are described here (Poirier et al. 2008). The rate of this catabolic process plays a clinically significant role in determining the efficiency of lipoprotein clearance from the blood." ;
